    <title>Next主题Pisces风格状态栏调整</title>
    <url>/2025/01/11/%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E6%A0%8F%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>使用Next主题的Pisces风格，不喜欢侧边导航栏，想改成横向的，网上没查到资料，于是自己摸索改了下。</p>
<p>1、找到主题_layout.njk文件，具体路径为Blog（博客跟目录）\themes\next\layout_layout.njk<br>2、找到以下代码，删除或注释导航栏代码</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;body itemscope itemtype=&quot;http://schema.org/WebPage&quot;&#123;% if theme.motion.enable %&#125; class=&quot;use-motion&quot;&#123;% endif %&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div class=&quot;headband&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;main class=&quot;main&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;column&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;header class=&quot;header&quot; itemscope itemtype=&quot;http://schema.org/WPHeader&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      &lt;!-- 下面这行是网站名字代码 --&gt; </span><br><span class="line">      &#123;%- include &#x27;_partials/header/brand.njk&#x27; -%&#125;   	 </span><br><span class="line">	 &lt;!-- 下面这行是导航栏代码，删除或注释 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     </span><br><span class="line">        &#123;%- include &#x27;_partials/header/index.njk&#x27; -%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		--&gt; </span><br><span class="line">      &lt;/header&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3、找到以下代码,在main-inner下面添加index.njk文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div class=&quot;main-inner &#123;% block class %&#125;&#123;% endblock %&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!--  下面是我自己添加部分  --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   &lt;div class=&quot;header-line&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">       &lt;header class=&quot;header-line&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &#123;%- include &#x27;_partials/header/index.njk&#x27; -%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">       &lt;/header&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;   </span><br><span class="line">&lt;!--  自己添加部分部分结束  --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;%- include &#x27;_partials/header/sub-menu.njk&#x27; -%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% block content %&#125;&#123;% endblock %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;%- include &#x27;_partials/comments.njk&#x27; -%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   &lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>4、自己设类选择器，然后在themes\next\source\css_schemes\Pisces_menu.styl中修改想要的样式。</p>
]]></content>
